Directed by Ali Abbas Zafar.

Written by Ali Abbas Zafar.

Cast Salman Khan(Sultan Ali Khan). Anushka Sharma(Aarfa). Randeep Hooda(Fateh Singh). Amit Sadh(Aakash Oberoi). Kumud Mishra(Barkat). Marrese Crump(Marrese). Parikshit Sahni(Gyan Singh Oberoi). Tyron Woodley(Tyron). Ron Smoorenburg(Ron). Brahim Chab(Brahim (as Brahim Achabbakhe)). Kubbra Sait(Kubra Sait (as Kubra Sait)). BjÃ¶rn Freiberg(Pilot). Durgesh Kumar(Commentator (uncredited)) . Asim(Titu’s Friend 2). Darshan Aulakh(Engine Driver). Rajesh Bharadwaj(Olympics Result Announcer). Himanshu Bhutiyani(Doctor Safdurjung). Meiyang Chang(Meiyang Chang). Shibani Dandekar(News Reporter). Danesh(Titu’s Friend 1). Abhishek Duhan(Titu). Farrukh Jaffar(Sultan’s grandmother). Anjana Om Kashyap(News Reporter). Kabir Khan(Advtisment’s Director). Ajeetpal Khatri(Bagga). Narendra Khatri(Sultan’s Assistant). Caroline Koziol(Nurse (as a different name)). Naveen Kumar(Sharief Ali Khan). Riteish Malik(Investor 1). Hans Marrero(MMA Fighter 1). Smriti Mishra(Nurse). Parvez Mullan(Vicky Kukreja’s Father). Pawan(Pawan). Ashish Raja(Rajbeer). Ivan Rodrigues(Mr. Patel). Sumeet Samnani(Vicky Kukreja). Anant Vidhaat Sharma(Govind). Satish Sharma(Minister). Vibhoutee Sharma(Self). Sumeil Sheikh(Interstate wrestler). Brij Shukla(Manjeet). Suzie(Sultan’s Daughter). B.L. Tandon(Haryanvi Tau). Monica Verma(Doctor). Arwind Wahi(Inter State Coach). Zane(PTD Fighter). Marko Zaror(Marcus)

Languages Hindi. English. Haryanvi.

Producers Umair Ahmad. Aditya Chopra. GyÃ¶rgy Czutor. Sudhanshu Kumar. Bharat Rawail. Aashish Singh. Arjun Singh. Navmeet Singh.

Production Yash Raj Films.
